						<p><hi rend="bold">King: [Tribhuvanachakravartin Rāja]rājadēva. Year 10: 1226 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record that, Kāśyapaṉ Muḍikoṇḍāṉ Duṟgaiyāṉ Śivalōkanāyagaṉ and other priests <hi rend="italic">(śivabrāhmaṇas)</hi> of Śrīmūlasthānam-uḍaiyār temple received gift from a certain Villavarājaṉ (for burning a lamp in the temple). Other details are lost.</p>						

